{"tid":2142991,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血公民黃兆健：大家在網上找到「出氣」的渠道，能夠妤解一下心中鬱悶，最好不過。公道看待熱狗工作，便已足夠。","createTime":"2020-08-06T21:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T13:49:37.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"56b2ebb49128f0db29ae0a441e1da95214a7a121","tid":2142991,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T21:22:02.000Z","msg":"黃兆健：<br />\n一般而言，小弟個人專頁每日會收到不少「藍絲」私訊謾罵；今日小弟在地區群組，呼籲更多朋友捐血救人後，收到圖上朋友的msg。<br />\n其實我不會介意，大家在網上找到「出氣」的渠道，能夠妤解一下心中鬱悶，最好不過。心理上健康同樣重要～<br />\n情緒穩定的朋友，請大家公道看待熱狗工作，便已足夠。&hearts;️<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt2bVAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt2bVAf.jpg&h=babfa1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e8deb0d8304eccfa801102c55bd6d608d7d2dde","tid":2142991,"uid":200135,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T21:25:32.000Z","msg":"其實諗緊熱狗係咪俾蟲泰搞壞哂個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry for 唔熟熱狗"},{"pid":"572ac07d34da86e971035fd7b88819dec4b276e8","tid":2142991,"uid":339751,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"4e8deb0d8304eccfa801102c55bd6d608d7d2dde","tid":2142991,"uid":200135,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T21:25:32.000Z","msg":"其實諗緊熱狗係咪俾蟲泰搞壞哂個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry for 唔熟熱狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T21:28:00.000Z","msg":"熱狗只係一班自以為看破世事既中二病毒撚<br />\n可以唔洗理呢啲傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2750b8fb615feafc915056b4e642b0fee13843f","tid":2142991,"uid":123264,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"572ac07d34da86e971035fd7b88819dec4b276e8","tid":2142991,"uid":339751,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"4e8deb0d8304eccfa801102c55bd6d608d7d2dde","tid":2142991,"uid":200